{"tid":1557690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖行街基本守則救你一命呀","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:06:38.000Z","uid":292783,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8bff129e9b04ef80ce41dbf53250e34c30cb6e","tid":1557690,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"求下你地<br />\n我知你地有心出黎各區行街拍拖，以下有D野係需要清楚知道<br />\n<br />\n1.手機解請解除面部解鎖同指紋解鎖<br />\n2.玩法轉左唔好再跳閘住<br />\n3.同你識既人講去左邊度拍拖同報到<br />\n4.打緊仗就唔好做低頭族<br />\n5.清楚突發離開既路線<br />\n6.商場之間通道會唔會落閘<br />\n7.手機要叉滿電備用<br />\n8.telegram一手group<br />\n9.關對話程式彈出通知畫面<br />\n10.iphone下載free app《Parachute》<br />\n11.被撲跌不等於死亡,起到身既希望你為左條命著想<br />\n12.舒適既鞋助你步伐加快<br />\n13.地鐵唔再安全,付費區隨時包抄<br />\n14.係地面一樣亦要小心橫街地鐵出口<br />\n15.萬一你已被圍 身上既野掉得就掉<br />\n16.仲有人跌銀包,可唔可以換左條褲佢<br />\n17.見到揸刀揸鎚仔唔該唔好再比佢傷人<br />\n18.如果你係中游位置走緊盡可能行快少少，你慢慢行前線就無位走好危險 <br />\n19.有好心人但唔好個個都信<br />\n20.防偷窺保護貼防昅mon"},{"pid":"c3558170289ae4d66cec552b647a59ff3d305882","tid":1557690,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"0556095e06866995279c9e1d987c8b756b3d9927","tid":1557690,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">借錢緊要還 咪俾錢中共</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=b28322ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Yes! US</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"eff2899a658c6431c89ed28a21ad2c60fa142565","tid":1557690,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:22:24.000Z","msg":"呢個重要 幫你推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b2b8937d60d8ba32495d17ff94bf4796f9641d","tid":1557690,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"4d4843e1838aa0d0292179097bf82d2c79526962","tid":1557690,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"0596c122fc2c47a1df88961e47eddbd593f3857a","tid":1557690,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"99639c4b2f3a26178ad842cbbc979c28ff32daef","tid":1557690,"uid":255880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdfa0846421f689d0e258533b9d84a8faad15904","tid":1557690,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:23:45.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到 幫你推10次"},{"pid":"46c77ba8e5d7346da6d15158c489fafb20d9418a","tid":1557690,"uid":220687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d2258046d18519268eaf689fdd9824f80dd074e","tid":1557690,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:23:55.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"97920c02c17f7744c6e270d0